  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Caroline Weston complains of a recurrent pain in her face, possibly neuralgia. She heard Mr. Pierpont preach. She lists the people who called on her. She discusses a case involving some colored people and a man named Avis. She mentions a meeting of the American Peace Society. She talks about her school. She tells of the organization of an anti-slavery society located in Heath, Mass. She mentions a man named Luther B. Lincoln.</subfield>
